    "• Other information -export information associated with document publishing.",
    "This study used 200 randomly selected research documents from the dataset to compute Cohen-Kappa inter-rater reliability to ensure the study's reliability.",
    "This was achieved by screening the title and abstract of the documents and thus, rating as relevant or not.",
    "For consistency, the rating was done independently by two researchers (BO and KZ) to ensure the publication (articles, conference proceedings, reviews, and conference reviews) is specific/related to TM, and within the year 2004 and 2023.",
